1
00:00:00,350 --> 00:00:22,869
This program is recorded at Delhi on 24 November 1973. Here Shri Mataji is replying to the questions of the “sadhakas” (seekers) during the ten-day series of lectures held at Delhi.

2
00:00:22,869 --> 00:00:31,590
Shri Mataji: …to your subject matter. I will just try to continue with my thoughts.

3
00:00:31,590 --> 00:00:42,100
And later on, if you have any problems, I’ll answer about them. But as I told you, it is an ocean, ocean of knowledge, and I have been speaking like this for five years.

4
00:00:42,100 --> 00:01:03,239
And some of them have been hearing Me for about five years. But still, everything I say, they want to record it and want to re-hear it and I don’t know, soI think it is all a bottomless pit.

5
00:01:03,239 --> 00:01:14,520
Now, what exactly Kundalini is? Let us start from this point, I will go one by one to different subjects.

6
00:01:14,520 --> 00:01:24,659
Just before Kundalini, let us know what is creation. Because without creation you do not understand the place of Kundalini.

7
00:01:24,659 --> 00:01:46,579
Which I will, in a very short form, tell. The entire creation, like the tree, is the manifestation of one seed, which we can call as “Brahmabeej” ( seed of Brahma).

8
00:01:46,579 --> 00:02:02,439
Is the seed of creation. Now every seed has a germinating power. In the same way, the Brahmabeej also has a germinating power.

9
00:02:02,439 --> 00:02:10,679
Now it’s a hypothesis for you. For all the scientific understanding, it is a hypothesis.

10
00:02:10,679 --> 00:02:25,000
But we can establish it later on by our experiments. So, it becomes a law and a scientific fact.

11
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:39,860
In the beginning, this seed, there is no beginning and end, but let us start from a stage, from where the seed becomes the tree and the tree becomes the seed.

12
00:02:39,860 --> 00:02:54,260
The seed vibrated first time, and the vibrations of Divine Love, which is the power of that seed of Brahma.

13
00:02:54,260 --> 00:03:07,049
Divine Love is awareness itself and is a power which has got electricity, magnetism and all material powers in It.

14
00:03:07,049 --> 00:03:17,720
Also, a power that thinks, regulates, plans and creates. You can’t conceive of such a power.

15
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:34,180
Because such a power does not exist in the material world. So, from the seed, the vibrations of awareness started.

16
00:03:34,180 --> 00:03:44,610
(I think you should put your hands like this so that your de-conditioning also goes on with my speech.

17
00:03:44,610 --> 00:03:54,599
) So, the vibrations of that Divine Love spread on all the sides of the seed and formed the surface.

18
00:03:54,599 --> 00:04:03,990
This is what we call as Shakti, is the power, the Divine Love. Or the Divine Power.

19
00:04:03,990 --> 00:04:37,800
So, the seed was separated. The seed of Brahma, which was abstract, in the sense that it was not manifesting in any material appearances, manifestations, the seed was separated from the Shakti, and we had two forces working, one was the Brahma itself as a seed and another as its power, as the Shakti.

20
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:46,950
They call it, the Shaivites call it as the Shiva and the Shakti. Vaishnavites call it as a Vishnu, Krishna and Radha.

21
00:04:46,950 --> 00:04:54,539
Whatever you call it, is not the point. Actually, we human beings only call them by names and separate them.

22
00:04:54,539 --> 00:05:17,229
But, actually, there were only two things that existed. The first, the Ishwara, the witness, the regulator, the supervisor, who was watching his own Shakti and the play of that Shakti.

23
00:05:17,229 --> 00:05:32,720
The Shakti started manifesting itself. But, the Ishwara is the supervisor; He is the witness and He is silent.

24
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:40,840
Shakti had three powers. How She manifested, how She came into being, is another subject.

25
00:05:40,840 --> 00:05:46,630
How She has managed it is another subject. But She has got three powers.

26
00:05:46,630 --> 00:06:02,900
First power is, through Her ego, which is an incarnating power. Second power is Her Divine power, and the third power is Her material power.

27
00:06:02,900 --> 00:06:22,490
Divine power throughout regulated, created the whole Universe. Shakti, by another movement, created three types of moods.

28
00:06:22,490 --> 00:06:41,250
Three moods She created by movement like that. Thrice She moved like that, around Her ego and these three moods were, like a mother, She had a desire to have a child.

29
00:06:41,250 --> 00:07:02,170
Desire! So, She created “Tamo guna”. Then She had to act on that, so, She created the “Rajo guna”, the activating force.

30
00:07:02,170 --> 00:07:05,650
And once she has created Her own creation, She wanted to reveal her love.

31
00:07:05,650 --> 00:07:13,680
So, the “Sattva guna” was created, the Revelation. She is the Mother.

32
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:30,930
If you can think of, She is the mother of all the mother. How a mother sees her child, She sees Her creation.

33
00:07:30,930 --> 00:07:38,539
First, She creates through the Divine power, acting on the material power, all the creation.

34
00:07:38,539 --> 00:07:52,860
And then, She comes again and again, again and again, in three different forms.

35
00:07:52,860 --> 00:08:00,010
She comes as a mother Herself. Then She is most powerful and expressive.

36
00:08:00,010 --> 00:08:07,680
As she has come you know as Nava-Durga She has come, as Mother Mary She has come, as Quan Yin She has come.

37
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:18,069
She has come in many forms in many parts of the world. She came as Muhammad’s daughter, She came as Nanaka’s sister, She came as Janaka’s daughter.

38
00:08:18,069 --> 00:08:23,570
Only one person all the time, coming in this world in different forms.

39
00:08:23,570 --> 00:08:31,650
When She comes only as a Mother, She is very different, and She is very dynamic.

40
00:08:31,650 --> 00:08:43,710
But, sometimes She comes as a wife and sometimes as a mother, then She is dormant.

41
00:08:43,710 --> 00:09:05,700
She acts, but She is not felt. Like, Radha of Krishna. Same Mother comes, again and again, incarnates to help the people to evolve out of this Bhavasagara, the void.

42
00:09:05,700 --> 00:09:19,459
She creates the Maya, She creates the illusion. Like a mother, like a mother bird who hides herself and calls her little one.

43
00:09:19,459 --> 00:09:26,600
The little birdie. So, the little bird can spread its wings to find the mother.

44
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:36,829
She creates all the illusion. And it is She only, who make you realise that it is all an illusion.

45
00:09:36,829 --> 00:09:48,340
She makes you feel that you are separate from Her. The “I” ness in you She develops Herself.

46
00:09:48,340 --> 00:09:52,750
And then She wants you to find out the means, the Mother, the all-pervading Chaitanya that is your Mother.

47
00:09:52,750 --> 00:10:04,810
And by this, doing this She matures you throughout and creates a beautiful instrument out of a human being.

48
00:10:04,810 --> 00:10:11,010
And then She reveals Her love and exposes Herself, Her love into your being.

49
00:10:11,010 --> 00:10:30,440
First, the material evolution took place as you know very well. I have spoken on that also.

50
00:10:30,440 --> 00:10:39,279
I would not like to touch that now. Then, up to the human level it has stopped.

51
00:10:39,279 --> 00:10:53,899
Now the human being has raised his body. The animal has not. But human being raised his body and his brain starts developing in a conical way.

52
00:10:53,899 --> 00:11:10,990
That conical structure gives it a prism-like quality, by which, the Chaitanya, the light, when it pours into the brain, goes into refraction.

53
00:11:10,990 --> 00:11:18,890
I hope you understand the word refraction. Means it passes through the prism, as you have seen, “kendrikaran” (centralisation) they call it.

54
00:11:18,890 --> 00:11:30,980
The rays are separated. Only in the human beings, the rays of Chaitanya are separated, and not in the animals.

55
00:11:30,980 --> 00:11:40,930
And the rays that pass through the center of the fontanelle bone here, which you call as “talu”, it is a very important thing.

56
00:11:40,930 --> 00:11:51,899
It passes through the apex of the brain and goes straight directly down to the medulla oblongata and settles down at the back of the triangular bone known as the coccyx.

57
00:11:51,899 --> 00:11:56,100
It is completely parasympathetic in its function, that is, it fills you up completely and that rests there as the residual consciousness.

58
00:11:56,100 --> 00:11:59,370
That is the Kundalini. Doctors may not agree today but they will have to agree one day.

59
00:11:59,370 --> 00:12:11,390
I can show you the breathing of the Kundalini in the coccyx. [Mother is talking aside to Sahaja Yogis].

60
00:12:11,390 --> 00:13:04,199
So, in the centre of this, in the centre of your head, at the coccyx, from there to the coccyx, is a line which goes down through the medulla oblongata and is known as the channel of“Sushumna”.

61
00:13:04,199 --> 00:13:26,839
The two other things that pass across like that, are sympathetic in nature because they are there to exhaust your energy, also, are known as sympathetic nervous system.

62
00:13:26,839 --> 00:13:44,510
But their channels are known as “Ida” and “Pingala”. So, the Mother Kundalini settles down (as) the residual consciousness in the coccyx.

63
00:13:44,510 --> 00:13:50,430
She is very well settled there, waiting for an opportunity to rise.

64
00:13:50,430 --> 00:14:01,730
And the opportunity is, when her child, she has only one child. And throughout his birth, she is following him.

65
00:14:01,730 --> 00:14:06,880
She is all the time there. When the child dies, her vacuum is created.

66
00:14:06,880 --> 00:14:13,230
And (when the child is born again), again she comes back in the same child.

67
00:14:13,230 --> 00:14:27,230
And she knows all the problems of the child. This Kundalini gives you the rebirth.

68
00:14:27,230 --> 00:14:46,949
You have heard about “dwijaha” the one who is twice-born. Every religion,every religion, I mean religion; I do not mean irreligion – every religion has preached that you have to be reborn.

69
00:14:46,949 --> 00:14:56,800
Those, who have not, are no religion. Religion in the Sanskrit language is “dharma”.

70
00:14:56,800 --> 00:15:03,570
Dharma means “dharaiticha dharma”, the one which you sustain. Whatever you sustain is the dharma.

71
00:15:03,570 --> 00:15:11,090
Still, sustain does’nt have that meaning, but still, you can say sustain.

72
00:15:11,090 --> 00:15:16,480
Because in the law ministry and all that, you hear this word, it is too much and so cheaply.

73
00:15:16,480 --> 00:15:24,690
But one that sustains is the dharma. Sustains what? Sustains the meeting of the all-pervading.

74
00:15:24,690 --> 00:15:41,780
Not the “jadugar ka kaam” (magician’s work), see the way that they go on “jadu, yahaan se nikaal diya, wahan se nikaal diya” (making things appear out of nowhere), all this thing are not dharma.

75
00:15:41,780 --> 00:15:48,330
Remember one thing that all these things are not dharma. Dharma is only the one that sustains the meeting of Atma (Spirit) with Paramatma (God Almighty).

76
00:15:48,330 --> 00:16:13,009
In the human being, in his heart, in every human being, in the heart of all the living beings, is the reflection of the Atma, which is of the Paramatma, which is the Ishwara, which I have told you about, He is reflected.

77
00:16:13,009 --> 00:16:19,290
And like a flicker of a flame, just like your thumb, it is there in your heart.

78
00:16:19,290 --> 00:16:31,870
Actually you, all your growth, creation, everything, is managed by your heart – not by your brain.

79
00:16:31,870 --> 00:16:40,699
In the seat of the heart, in the centre of the heart. [Inaudible/someone asks a question].

80
00:16:40,699 --> 00:16:44,019
No, no, I will tell you what. Your point is all right. The doctor says the heart is here.

81
00:16:44,019 --> 00:16:52,630
The heart is the organ. The heart is the organ, which is looked after by the cardiac plexus.

82
00:16:52,630 --> 00:17:05,070
So, part of the cardiac plexus is looking after the heart. Because cardiac plexus has got many sub-plexuses.

83
00:17:05,070 --> 00:17:15,880
Out of which, except for four of them, the rest of them, that is, the heart has got twelve sub-plexuses.

84
00:17:15,880 --> 00:17:31,400
Out of which eight of them are looking after the heart. Four of them, other things, I mean, there is a mixture of all these things, some of them are looking after the heart and some of them are looking after the mind.

85
00:17:31,400 --> 00:17:46,280
But this light is in your heart, in the organ heart – not in the plexus.

86
00:17:46,280 --> 00:17:58,020
Plexus is for the play of the Kundalini. But the Kundalini moves in such a way that she goes to the heart later on and the enlightenment takes place.

87
00:17:58,020 --> 00:18:13,210
The spark starts from there. And when we raise your Kundalini through Sahaja Yoga, the system is followed like this, the Kundalini rises because of a certain condition being filled.

88
00:18:13,210 --> 00:18:23,230
There is a gap in your Sushumna, which is shown outside also, that below the heart, the vagus nerve ends abruptly.

89
00:18:23,230 --> 00:18:32,159
And up to the aortic plexus, there is a void. If there is a doctor, he will understand it.

90
00:18:32,159 --> 00:18:51,110
This void is to be filled by the same Divine love. If somebody, who has got the Divine love flowing through her or his being, then such a person can pour that love, that water of love for your seeking journey.

91
00:18:51,110 --> 00:18:57,820
This is the condition of Sahaja Yoga. That is why a person who is not realised cannot do this.

92
00:18:57,820 --> 00:19:09,290
Even a realised person may not be able to do this. Because he must be at a certain stage of that Divine love by which he can give realisation.

93
00:19:09,290 --> 00:19:17,670
For example, we have given realisation to thousands of people both here and abroad and also awakening to, I do not know how many thousands.

94
00:19:17,670 --> 00:19:31,380
But out of them, only eleven people so far can give realisation. And they know the technique of giving the realisation and telling the people how to maintain it.

95
00:19:31,380 --> 00:19:46,450
Only eleven in these five years. The day I have a thousand like you, no problem.

96
00:19:46,450 --> 00:19:52,070
I need a thousand hands to fight the war between the dharma and adharma.

97
00:19:52,070 --> 00:19:59,120
Dharma can be established. But the only problem of Sahaja Yoga is that you have to be completely independent and free.

98
00:19:59,120 --> 00:20:07,940
And that you must choose it by your will. Your will will be respected till the end.

99
00:20:07,940 --> 00:20:13,980
If you have no will to have it, you cannot have it. It is not enticement or mesmerism by which I can do it.

100
00:20:13,980 --> 00:20:14,980
So naturally, it will have to work slowly, gradually, according to your will.

101
00:20:14,980 --> 00:20:20,470
If you do not have the will, I am going to respect you as a mother respects her grown-up son.

102
00:20:20,470 --> 00:20:27,850
It is for you to decide to have it. It is in your will, you get the experience and you are sure of it.

103
00:20:27,850 --> 00:20:39,200
And once you get it, there is no doubt left in your mind. You know that.

104
00:20:39,200 --> 00:21:02,330
Beg pardon?[Inaudible/question about method]. Shri Mataji: Now, in this? There are different and different types of people and different types of things they have done to their own Kundalini.

105
00:21:02,330 --> 00:21:08,700
The problem is how far you have kept your Kundalini alright. It is very important.

106
00:21:08,700 --> 00:21:13,370
Because it falls in many places. We have seen, we are trying to pull it up and it’s going down.

107
00:21:13,370 --> 00:21:20,289
But nothing will happen to you. You will not know a thing. Now, the method to be followed, I tell you that later on, with that course I will tell you.

108
00:21:20,289 --> 00:21:34,240
Now, the method to be followed is not your job. Is not your job. It is to be done by the Divine Love itself.

109
00:21:34,240 --> 00:21:39,700
Why should you worry? You never asked to be created. You never asked for all this headache.

110
00:21:39,700 --> 00:21:44,150
Why should you worry about these things? Let the Divine look after you.

111
00:21:44,150 --> 00:21:51,169
But, in our ignorance, as human beings are, most of them are very ignorant people.

112
00:21:51,169 --> 00:21:59,909
They may be very learned. We feel we are carrying the load of the world on our heads.

113
00:21:59,909 --> 00:22:04,160
The other day, as I told you a joke, that some villagers who were going by plane.

114
00:22:04,160 --> 00:22:18,010
They were told not to carry such a lot of luggage. When they took their seats, they put all the luggage on their heads.

115
00:22:18,010 --> 00:22:37,500
And when they were asked, “Why are you putting the luggage on your head?”, they said, “Oh, we are trying to reduce the weight of the aeroplane”.

116
00:22:37,500 --> 00:23:05,570
The One who has created you, the One who is doing everything, the One who is pulsating your heart, every moment every minute he is looking after your breathing.

117
00:23:05,570 --> 00:23:26,360
What can you do? What method do you have to produce one plant out of one seed? One.

118
00:23:26,360 --> 00:23:35,299
I say, one. Human beings have no method to do anything that is living.

119
00:23:35,299 --> 00:23:51,570
But, in our ignorance, we think that we are doing something. We are doing nothing whatsoever.

120
00:23:51,570 --> 00:24:04,919
We have to be the tool of the Divine. That is why we are born on Earth.

121
00:24:04,919 --> 00:24:19,779
And Sahaja Yoga itself means Sahaja, means, born with you. Now, you know what do you do to digest your food? Nothing.

122
00:24:19,779 --> 00:24:34,120
What do we do to make our heartbeat? Nothing. In the same way, you do nothing to get realisation.

123
00:24:34,120 --> 00:24:46,539
Actually, this is a fact. And what do I do? I just love you. That’s all.

124
00:24:46,539 --> 00:24:59,890
If I say I love you, you might think it is a relative term, it is not.

125
00:24:59,890 --> 00:25:13,340
It is like the sunshine. As the sun shines on you, My love shines on you.

126
00:25:13,340 --> 00:25:16,490
And the love pour into your being, deconditions you, and that void is filled, and the Kundalini rises in her glory.

127
00:25:16,490 --> 00:25:18,490
But so far, all the other Kundalini jagruti (awakening) you might have heard about, you just forget them.

128
00:25:18,490 --> 00:25:21,490
[Inaudible/someone asks or comments]. Oh, just forget. They are so confused, to such an extent.

129
00:25:21,490 --> 00:25:23,490
You may have read very, very big books, I know. So many people have written, and I used to laugh at them.

130
00:25:23,490 --> 00:25:25,490
Now, some, they are so much confused that they do not know that Mooladhara is separated very much from Mooladhara chakra.

131
00:25:25,490 --> 00:25:27,490
It is a very important point you have brought out. I wish I could tell you because you are all matured people.

132
00:25:27,490 --> 00:25:29,490
Mooladhara is the coccyx where the Kundalini mother is sitting there; your holy mother is sitting.

133
00:25:29,490 --> 00:25:32,490
Mother is a holy thing. You are already sublimated. You are not to be sublimated.

134
00:25:32,490 --> 00:25:33,490
Those who talk of sex sublimation are foolish people, they have no idea.

135
00:25:33,490 --> 00:25:34,490
You are already having your mother seated there, just waiting for this little happening.

136
00:25:34,490 --> 00:25:36,490
Mooladhara chakra is the only chakra in which is outside the medulla oblongata and is seated at a point from where it also controls your sex.

137
00:25:36,490 --> 00:25:38,490
Sex is something like we have got an outlet in our household, “mori” (Marathi meaning sink).

138
00:25:38,490 --> 00:25:39,490
A little of that energy flows there and it is settled at Mooladhara chakra.

139
00:25:39,490 --> 00:25:46,000
Finished. Do we, when we want to drink water, do we pump out that mori and put up that water there – even if we do not have water to drink? How can you have evolution this way by going through sex? Sex has nothing to do with Kundalini, I can assure you that.

140
00:25:46,000 --> 00:25:56,080
On the contrary, those who try these tricks, putting the sex on their mother, are insulting their mother to such an extent that she gets angry and annoyed.

141
00:25:56,080 --> 00:26:04,090
And her temper which crawls on your sympathetic nervous system gives you all these horrible experiences of shouting, screaming, jumping and all doing all kinds of things.

142
00:26:04,090 --> 00:26:14,760
She is your mother. As an Indian, you can understandwhat is a mother Now that Freud was another of rakshasa who preached all these nonsensical things about human beings.

143
00:26:14,760 --> 00:26:18,750
He only knew about libido, he had not the complete knowledge about human beings.

144
00:26:18,750 --> 00:26:33,190
He just discussed libido. And with libido, he confused Kundalini, and he is talking about all these suppressed feelings which are nothing but expression and manifestation of the libido.

145
00:26:33,190 --> 00:26:44,399
Libido is just a part on the side which we call as Pingala Nadi. He has ruined the American mind by talking about this.

146
00:26:44,399 --> 00:26:48,460
And the American mothers, poor things are completely crushed under it.

147
00:26:48,460 --> 00:26:54,830
At least, thank God in India, we do not have this problem. We have many others but not this.

148
00:26:54,830 --> 00:26:59,679
Americans have solved lots of their problems and are now on the brink of realisation.

149
00:26:59,679 --> 00:27:05,650
But the only problem is this Mr Freud who has put wrong ideas into their heads about their mothers.

150
00:27:05,650 --> 00:27:13,330
If that was not there, it is a wonderful place and beautiful people just seeking realisation.

151
00:27:13,330 --> 00:27:21,080
About to get realisation. So, we as Indians understand what our mother is and putting the sex on her.

152
00:27:21,080 --> 00:27:36,179
Except for Jung, who was right disciple, who has refuted allhis charges many a times and written books after books against this kind of attitude, one-sided attitude of Freud.

153
00:27:36,179 --> 00:27:50,360
But few people have read Jung. That’s the tragedy. But as it is, now this is the wrong type of Kundalini sadhana as they call it.

154
00:27:50,360 --> 00:28:01,570
She never gets angry. You do not know how much she loves. She loves you more than I do.

155
00:28:01,570 --> 00:28:09,960
When I try to raise your Kundalini, she says first cure my child. This is the problem of my child of previous birth.

156
00:28:09,960 --> 00:28:13,570
This is the problem of my child of this birth. Physically this is the problem.

157
00:28:13,570 --> 00:28:16,549
Will you please first cure the child? So, I have to jolly well cure you, otherwise, she will not come up.

158
00:28:16,549 --> 00:28:33,049
[Inaudible/question about the position of Kundalini]. Now, her position in the medulla oblongata is the coccyx in the triangular bone, where she sits in three and a half coils.

159
00:28:33,049 --> 00:28:39,419
Which you can see also, later on. When you are realised and go to a certain state.

160
00:28:39,419 --> 00:28:47,860
And when you have got it, through your parasympathetic and you can go your sympathetic and see all these things.

161
00:28:47,860 --> 00:28:55,830
They are so confused, if you read their books, don’t you find they are very much confused? About their positions and everything that they talk about.

162
00:28:55,830 --> 00:29:02,110
Some say the Mooladhara chakra is here and some say it is there. How can that be? Truth is only one.

163
00:29:02,110 --> 00:29:08,160
[Inaudible/Tantriks?] Tantriks are another type, I do not know what to call them.

164
00:29:08,160 --> 00:29:21,970
They are harming themselves and all the rest of the world. And they will take ages to get realisation.

165
00:29:21,970 --> 00:29:37,020
Ages. It’s a sin they are committing. All the tantrikas. What is a shakti without love? There is no shakti without love.

166
00:29:37,020 --> 00:29:44,390
Tantriks do not know where they are, what they are doing. They are just doing it.

167
00:29:44,390 --> 00:29:50,059
Now, as far as Kundalini is concerned, I have covered that topic. Now, about tantrikas, as he has come, let me talk about libido because that he is interested.

168
00:29:50,059 --> 00:29:59,240
But what about meditation then? Should we talk about tantrikas tomorrow? All: Tomorrow.

169
00:29:59,240 --> 00:30:02,820
Shri Mataji: On Libido because we must have the experience, that is the main thing.

170
00:30:02,820 --> 00:30:12,370
Because meditation is the most important. Realised, those who are realised understand the importance of Realisation.

171
00:30:12,370 --> 00:30:20,159
Because talks are talks, reading is reading and Divine is Divine. You cannot reach there with your thoughts or reading.

172
00:30:20,159 --> 00:30:49,700
On the contrary, those who have read too much, it is very difficult for me to make them understand this is all “avidya” (false knowledge How do you describe your Mother in words? Have you got enough words to even describe the material mother you have? Then how can you understand that Divine, which is the mother of all the mothers.

173
00:30:49,700 --> 00:31:08,250
It is for you to feel that love and jump into the ocean of that love which is knowledge, complete knowledge.

174
00:31:08,250 --> 00:31:08,750
And beauty.

